data.description: Convenient location in great southwest neighborhood. All brick, solid 1 story home built by Saliba. Beautiful hardwood floors. Granite countertops. Side entry 2 car garage. Split bedrooms. Open concept kitchen/dining/grandroom. HVAC new 2021. Mud room off garage with preacher's bench leads to nice size laundry room, primary bedroom and grandroom. Shady backyard to block western sun. Covered front porch & back patio. Floored storage above garage. All Dothan utilities. Move in ready. Well maintained home.
